<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Send an Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 70%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        input[type="text"], input[type="email"], textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .email-template {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <br><br>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-template">
            <strong>Mail to:</strong> <i><%= vol_email %></i><br><br>
            <strong>Subject:</strong> Volunteer Opportunity in (city name) on (event date)<br><br>
            Hi <%= volunteer_name %>,<br><br>
            This is Jen from the Turtle Shelter Project. Thank you again so much for your willingness to volunteer with us!
            We have an upcoming event in (city name), (state name) that will take place on (event date), at (event time).<br><br>
            We would love to know if you're available to participate with us!<br><br>
            Please let us know if you can make it by responding to this email.<br><br>
            Thank you,<br>
            Jen<br><br>
            <i>The Turtle Shelter Project</i>
            <br>
            <i>turtleshelterproject@gmail.com</i>
            <br>
            <i>(801)-872-3190</i>
            <br>
            <!--JUN I need you to insert logo here-->
            <img src="/images/TransparentTSPLogo.png" alt="TSP Logo" width="50px" height="50px">
        </div>
        <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox?compose=new" 
        target="_blank">
            <button type="button">Send Email</button>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
